      <title>美国正在危险的时候退出全球健康</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/the-consequences-of-trump-s-cdc-overhaul-who-exit-worry-scientists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普对CDC的大修使科学家担心流感，麻疹甚至埃博拉病毒。]]></description>
